    <title type="html"><![CDATA[新手培养日记(二)]]></title>
    <link href="http://agiledon.github.com/blog/2013/03/28/diary-2-for-coaching-fresh-man/"/>
    <updated>2013-03-28T20:30:00+08:00</updated>
